[30;1m13 | [0m[35mpywinauto[0m
[30;1m14 | [0m[35m============[0m
[30;1m15 | [0m[35mpywinauto is a set of python modules to automate the Microsoft Windows GUI. [0m
[30;1m16 | [0m[35mAt its simplest it allows you to send mouse and keyboard actions to windows [0m
[30;1m17 | [0m[35mdialogs and controls, but it has support for more complex actions like getting text data.[0m
[30;1m18 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m19 | [0m[35mSupported technologies under the hood: Win32 API (`backend="win32"`; used by default),[0m
